# Wild Trails Design System Rules

## UI Components

### Always Use Reusable Components
- Import from `@/app/components/ui`
- Available: Button, Input, GlassPanel, Icon, Skeleton, Toast
- Don't create one-off button/input styles

### Class Name Management
```tsx
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils";

// Use cn() for all className concatenation
className={cn("base-classes", condition && "conditional", className)}
```

### Component Patterns
- All components use `React.forwardRef`
- Export TypeScript interfaces
- Set `displayName` for debugging
- Support `className` prop for customization

## Theme Colors

### Primary Brand
```tsx
bg-primary           // #13ec13 (vibrant green)
bg-primary-dark      // #0fb80f
text-primary
border-primary
```

### Backgrounds
```tsx
bg-background-dark        // #102210 (main dark bg)
bg-surface-dark           // #1a2c1a (card bg)
bg-surface-dark-elevated  // #283928 (elevated elements)
```

### Glass Effects
```tsx
<GlassPanel>           // Use instead of custom cards
<GlassPanel variant="light">  // For light theme
```

## Typography

### Font Families
```tsx
font-display    // Be Vietnam Pro (headings, bold text)
font-body       // Noto Sans (body text, UI)
```

### Headings
```tsx
<h1 className="text-4xl font-black text-white">  // Use font-black for impact
<h2 className="text-2xl font-bold text-white">
```

## Icons

### Always Use Icon Component
```tsx
import { Icon } from "@/app/components/ui";

<Icon name="terrain" size="lg" className="text-primary" />
```

### Common Icons
- `terrain` - Brand/logo
- `add_location` - Create game
- `group_add` - Join game
- `list` - My games
- `play_arrow` - Start/resume
- `settings` - Configuration
- `close` - Close/cancel

## Buttons

### Variants
```tsx
<Button variant="primary">    // Main actions (green)
<Button variant="secondary">  // Secondary actions (border)
<Button variant="ghost">      // Subtle actions
<Button variant="outline">    // Alternative border style
```

### With Icons
```tsx
<Button variant="primary">
  <Icon name="add" className="mr-2" />
  Create Game
</Button>
```

## Forms

### Use Input Component
```tsx
<Input
  label="Game Name"
  placeholder="My Adventure"
  error={errors.name}
  value={name}
  onChange={handleChange}
/>
```

### Radio/Select Styling
```tsx
// For custom radio buttons
className="h-12 rounded-lg border-2 border-white/10 bg-surface-dark-elevated 
  peer-checked:border-primary peer-checked:bg-primary/10"

// For selects
className="h-12 rounded-lg border bg-surface-dark-elevated text-white 
  border-white/10 px-4 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary"
```

## Layouts

### Page Structure
```tsx
<main className="min-h-screen dark:bg-background-dark relative">
  {/* Background pattern */}
  <div className="absolute inset-0 z-0">...</div>
  
  {/* Content */}
  <div className="relative z-10 p-4 md:p-8">
    <GlassPanel className="p-6 lg:p-8">
      {/* Your content */}
    </GlassPanel>
  </div>
</main>
```

### Responsive Breakpoints
- `sm:` 640px (mobile landscape)
- `md:` 768px (tablet)
- `lg:` 1024px (desktop)

### Touch Targets
- Minimum height: `h-12` (48px) for mobile
- Buttons use: `h-9` (sm), `h-12` (md), `h-14` (lg)

## Animations

### Built-in Classes
```tsx
animate-fade-in        // Fade in
animate-fade-in-up     // Fade + slide up
animate-slide-up       // Slide up
animate-scale-in       // Scale in
animate-pulse          // Pulse (for skeletons)
```

### Hover Effects
```tsx
hover:scale-[1.02]     // Subtle scale up
hover:bg-primary/10    // Subtle bg change
transition-all         // Smooth transitions
```

## Accessibility

### Always Include
- Focus rings: `focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary`
- Disabled states: `disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed`
- ARIA labels for icon-only buttons
- Semantic HTML (button, input, nav, etc.)

### Icon Buttons
```tsx
<Button variant="ghost" aria-label="Close">
  <Icon name="close" />
</Button>
```

## Toast Notifications

### Usage
```tsx
import { useToast } from "@/app/components/ui";

const { showToast } = useToast();

showToast("success", "Game created successfully!");
showToast("error", "Failed to save");
showToast("warning", "Location access required");
showToast("info", "Hint unlocked");
```

## Loading States

### Use Skeleton
```tsx
import { Skeleton, GameCardSkeleton } from "@/app/components/ui";

{loading ? <GameCardSkeleton /> : <GameCard />}
{loading ? <Skeleton width="200px" height="40px" /> : <Content />}
```

## Don't

- ❌ Don't use emoji in buttons (use Icon component)
- ❌ Don't hardcode colors (use theme classes)
- ❌ Don't use string concatenation for classes (use `cn()`)
- ❌ Don't create custom button styles (use Button variants)
- ❌ Don't use inline styles (use Tailwind)
- ❌ Don't forget focus states on interactive elements

## Do

- ✅ Use `cn()` for all className logic
- ✅ Use Icon component for all icons
- ✅ Use Button component with variants
- ✅ Use GlassPanel for cards/containers
- ✅ Test components with React Testing Library
- ✅ Ensure mobile responsiveness (test at 320px+)
- ✅ Add focus states and ARIA labels
